    "name": "Turbo Fat",
    "steam_appid": 2213410,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213410/extras/4ab82196d23150f6c3f68e56a74fea92.poster.avif?t=1729011915\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213410/extras/4ab82196d23150f6c3f68e56a74fea92.webm?t=1729011915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213410/extras/4ab82196d23150f6c3f68e56a74fea92.mp4?t=1729011915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Turbo Fat</i> reimagines classic 90s block-stacking games with a delicious twist -- new pieces, new moves, new ways to score, and tons of wacky level gimmicks! Misdrop? Just squish your way out of it! Build insane combos with no limits, 10, 20 or even 100 lines! But don't wait for line pieces, we got rid of those! (Hey, nobody said it would be easy...)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213410/extras/cdde7b6ea775822507bb837c1bf7b238.webp?t=1729011915\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213410/extras/cdde7b6ea775822507bb837c1bf7b238.poster.avif?t=1729011915\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=21 /></picture></span><strong> Fun and Forgiving for New Puzzlers </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213410/extras/cdde7b6ea775822507bb837c1bf7b238.webp?t=1729011915\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213410/extras/cdde7b6ea775822507bb837c1bf7b238.poster.avif?t=1729011915\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=21 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Turbo Fat, there's no such thing as a bad move! Squish pieces through tight spaces and recover from misdrops with ease. Filling up your playfield is fine, too! You don't have to start over. And a helpful set of tutorials walks you through every step, making sure you're ready for the sweetest challenges ahead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213410/extras/3cf45b3377b150dbdad1893df763ae6f.webp?t=1729011915\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213410/extras/3cf45b3377b150dbdad1893df763ae6f.poster.avif?t=1729011915\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=21 /></picture></span><strong> Extreme Challenges for Puzzle Pros </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213410/extras/3cf45b3377b150dbdad1893df763ae6f.webp?t=1729011915\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213410/extras/3cf45b3377b150dbdad1893df763ae6f.poster.avif?t=1729011915\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=21 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready to prove your puzzle prowess? <i>Turbo Fat</i>’s toughest levels demand expert strategy and lightning-fast reflexes! Stack pieces into high-scoring cakes and chain massive combos to keep your customers happy (and full!) With ultra-responsive controls, you can move and lock pieces the moment they spawn, unlocking incredible high-speed possibilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213410/extras/01ca9c9aaf6126deb1117a1b6118213e.webp?t=1729011915\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213410/extras/01ca9c9aaf6126deb1117a1b6118213e.poster.avif?t=1729011915\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=21 /></picture></span><strong> There's Something for Everyone </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213410/extras/01ca9c9aaf6126deb1117a1b6118213e.webp?t=1729011915\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213410/extras/01ca9c9aaf6126deb1117a1b6118213e.poster.avif?t=1729011915\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=21 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With over 100 levels packed with unique twists, <i>Turbo Fat</i> offers something for every type of player! Refine your strategies in Training mode, then tackle Adventure mode to unlock new regions, meet quirky characters, and grow your restaurant empire, one cake at a time. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sprawling Story. </strong>The game's unique Adventure mode gives you a new selection of levels each time you play. Progress through 6 distinct regions, unlocking over 100 levels with their own cutscenes and characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Clever Levels.</strong> Discover over 100 wildly inventive levels, each packed with surprises and unique gimmicks to keep you on your toes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Different ways to practice. </strong>Master your skills with Training Modes like Score Attack and Time Attack, or relax in Sandbox Mode for endless, stress-free fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cute creatures.</strong> Mix and match over 80 creature parts to craft your unique monsters, or meet quirky community-created characters in the story and puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Banging tunes.</strong> An original 19-song soundtrack composed by Pete Ellison of Diskowarp Records -- it'll keep your toes tapping while you play!</p>",
